#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/tshoot-logintimeout.adoc:30
msgid ""
"For example, to change the timeout value to one hour, set the value in "
"[path]``rhn.conf`` to 3600 seconds, and the value in [path]``web.xml`` to 60 "
"minutes."
